Bypass Ward			KEY:Balanced Scale ~ Bypass Ward		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																DESC:You can pick the lock of even a magically locked door (such as one sealed by Arcane Lock or Hold Portal). The Open Lock DC for the door is considered 10 higher than normal due to the effect of the warding spell. You also gains a +2 sacred bonus to Open Lock checks. As a full-round action, you can make an Open Lock check to disable a magical trap (such as a Glyph of Warding) for 1 minute.																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.54
